		<tr>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				1. Yes..in fact I encourage it. =) <br> 2. Vallon Zek and Tallon Zek are Coin Only loot..Rallos is Balls to the walls one item loot. <br> 3. Coin Only loot-you can only loot coin off them. <br>    One Item loot- Coin and one item fromt heir body.(no weapons or shields or anything in bag <br> 4. Not if your killed by a player,no. <br> 5. On Vallon and Tallon Zek theres a 8 level difference..on Rallos Zek theres a 4 level difference.  <br> 6. Yes there's plenty of classes that allow you to &quot;solo&quot; play. <br> 7. There isnt that much kiling going on..some people play like normal some PK (or player kill) <br> 8. No but on Rallos Zek guards will protect you if they like you. <br>  <br> 		

